@startuml
title Figure 21. Web Voice Job Assistant Activity Diagram
start
:Visually impaired user\nactivates microphone on web;
:Browser captures speech input;
:Speech is converted to text;
:Backend sends text to AI\nfor intent extraction;

if (Intent extracted successfully?) then (Yes)
  :Build search conditions;
  :Query suitable jobs from database;
  :Generate concise response text;
  :Return job suggestions to web client;
  :Read response aloud via TTS;
  stop
else (No)
  :Return fallback message\nasking user to repeat;
  stop
endif
@enduml
